Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不!我讨厌你们\N{\rENG}No! I hate you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我才不告诉你们融合簇的任何信息呢\N{\rENG}I'm not telling you anything about the cluster.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,搞毛\N{\rENG}Oh, come on.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.71,0:00:45.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是像一大团,呃,即食麦片吗?\N{\rENG}Is it like a big, uh, hunk of granola?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.98,0:00:47.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么是即食麦片?\N{\rENG}What's granola?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.64,0:00:49.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很确定那不是即食麦片\N{\rENG}I'm sure it's not granola.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着,橄榄石,\N{\rENG}Now, Peridot,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我确定我们能达成一定共识\N{\rENG}I'm sure we can reach some sort of agreement.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许我们来做个交易?\N{\rENG}Perhaps a trade is in order?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.06,0:00:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,真好\N{\rENG}Oh, sure.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么不给我\N{\rENG}Why don't you just give me back\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.15,0:01:00.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的腿部和臂部增强器?\N{\rENG}my leg enhancements and my arm attachments\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.13,0:01:02.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}外加我的显示屏和日志和所有的信息?\N{\rENG}with my screen and my log and all my information.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.73,0:01:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,等等,你毁了它们!\N{\rENG}Oh, wait, you destroyed them!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以,不,我不认为我们能达成某种共识!\N{\rENG}So, no, I don't think we can reach some sort of agreement!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.35,0:01:13.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,橄榄石,你可以转身了\N{\rENG}Okay, Peridot, you can turn around now.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.04,0:01:19.41,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很抱歉打断你们的审讯\N{\rENG}Sorry for interrupting your interrogation.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.53,0:01:20.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要担心,史蒂文\N{\rENG}Don't worry about it, Steven.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.97,0:01:24.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我发誓,橄榄石随时都会招供的\N{\rENG}I swear, Peridot is gonna crack any second now.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我永远不会像你们招供的,\N{\rENG}I'll never crack for the likes of you,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们这群...水晶草包!\N{\rENG}you...Crystal clods.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.66,0:01:32.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦～,你的草包们可就在门口,你个小-\N{\rENG}Ooh, I got your clods right here, you little --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等,珍珠\N{\rENG}hold on, Pearl.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果她不愿意提供任何帮助的话\N{\rENG}If she's not gonna be of any help.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我们自己来调查这件事\N{\rENG}Let's investigate this thing on our own.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.75,0:01:37.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会跟你一起做的\N{\rENG}I'll come with you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.84,0:01:38.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起,史蒂文\N{\rENG}Sorry, Steven.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们需要你呆在家里\N{\rENG}We're gonna need you to stay here\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看管我们的...贵宾\N{\rENG}and keep an eye on our...Guest.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的?\N{\rENG}Really?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.22,0:01:46.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对,确保她不会搞幺蛾子\N{\rENG}Yeah. Make sure she doesn't try anything.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.42,0:01:47.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别担心\N{\rENG}Don't worry.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她失去肢端增强器后没什么威胁\N{\rENG}She's harmless without her limb enhancers\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我才不是毫无威胁呢!\N{\rENG}I'm not harmless!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.86,0:01:52.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,给我闭嘴!\N{\rENG}Oh, hush up!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.35,0:01:53.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Oh, Steven!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有一件事我得提\N{\rENG}There's one more thing I have to mention.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.24,0:01:55.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是什么?\N{\rENG}What is it?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.71,0:01:58.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我爱你,拜拜\N{\rENG}I love you. Bye.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}待会见\N{\rENG}See ya later.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯～\N{\rENG}Mm.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你得知道,她们走了,你现在可以出来了\N{\rENG}They left, you know. You can come out now.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,我-我喜欢在里面\N{\rENG}No. I-I like it in here.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔,看来真要下雨了\N{\rENG}Wow. It's really coming down.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}开始了!\N{\rENG}It's happening!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.51,0:02:26.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-融合簇!\N{\rENG}-The cluster!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的?\N{\rENG}Really?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有什么能制造那么恐怖的-\N{\rENG}What else could be making that horrible --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊啊!它在内部拍击着地球\N{\rENG}Aah! It's pounding on the earth from the inside.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是世界末日了\N{\rENG}This is it. This is the end of the world.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,那只是闪电而已\N{\rENG}Oh, that's just thunder.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错,一切都还正常\N{\rENG}Yeah, everything is fine.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那只是闪电,跟着雨一起出现\N{\rENG}It's just thunder. It happens when it rains.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...蛤?\N{\rENG}Eh...Huh?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不知道雨?\N{\rENG}You don't know about rain?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}离开我的屏幕,我什么都不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know anything without my screen.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这没什么\N{\rENG}It's okay.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看,假设汤是大海\N{\rENG}Here, pretend this soup is the ocean.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.77,0:02:57.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当太阳加热汤时,\N{\rENG}When the sun warms it up,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.21,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}水被蒸发,形成云\N{\rENG}the water evaporates into clouds,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.21,0:03:00.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就如同这蒸汽\N{\rENG}like this steam.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而当云变得非常重时,就开始下雨了\N{\rENG}And when the clouds get really heavy, it rains.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以滚烫的液体从天上倾泻而下?\N{\rENG}So scalding liquid pours down from the sky?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,不,只是水而已,那伤害不了你\N{\rENG}No, no, it's just water. It can't hurt you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来,为什么不让我给你展示一下呢?\N{\rENG}Here, why don't I just show you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,等等!\N{\rENG}Steven, wait!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来吧!\N{\rENG}Come on!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看,我很好,这只是水而已\N{\rENG}Look, I'm okay. It's just water.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这只是地球上发生的正常现象\N{\rENG}This is just something that happens on earth.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很凉爽吧?\N{\rENG}Isn't it cool?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.62,0:03:38.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}爽!\N{\rENG}Yeah!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}太好了,你做到了!\N{\rENG}Yeah, you did it!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你感觉怎么样?是不是很凉爽?\N{\rENG}What do you think? Isn't it cool?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}凉爽\N{\rENG}Cool.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.75,0:04:04.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真有趣\N{\rENG}That was fun.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.15,0:04:05.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈?\N{\rENG}Huh?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那...凑合吧\N{\rENG}It was...Something.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.80,0:04:09.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯...\N{\rENG}Hmm.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.82,0:04:10.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...\N{\rENG}Uh...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯...\N{\rENG}Mm...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Steven?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.55,0:04:14.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯?\N{\rENG}Hm?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要宣布一件事情\N{\rENG}I'm going to say something.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...为什么?\N{\rENG}Uh...What for?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为你向我解释了"雨"\N{\rENG}For explaining this "rain" business to me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,没关系\N{\rENG}Oh, no problem.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有关系,你是个非常有智慧的生物\N{\rENG}Yes. You're a much more intelligent creature\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}相比于我的预期的话\N{\rENG}than I initially thought.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,那挺好啊\N{\rENG}Uh, that's good.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.04,0:04:34.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错\N{\rENG}Yes.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有很多...用处,相比那些草包\N{\rENG}Much more...Useful than those clods.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,我决定了!\N{\rENG}Steven, I've made up my mind!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}决定什么?\N{\rENG}About what, exactly?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我决定和你分享一些信息\N{\rENG}I've decided to share some information with you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊,我早知道你用了我的牙刷\N{\rENG}Ah, I know you use my toothbrush.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不-不\N{\rENG}N-no.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,没错\N{\rENG}Well, yes.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这是关于融合簇的\N{\rENG}But it's about the cluster.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你招了\N{\rENG}You cracked.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我才没招呢!\N{\rENG}I haven't cracked!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等,你得告诉宝石人们,她们得知道\N{\rENG}Wait, you have to tell the gems. They need to know this.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,我才不要和她们说呢\N{\rENG}No, I don't want to talk to them.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是我需要的唯一的一个\N{\rENG}You're the only one I need.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可以现在告诉你,但我缺少材料\N{\rENG}I could show you now, but I have nothing.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的臂部增强件,我的手指,我的屏幕,我的日志-\N{\rENG}My arm attachments, my fingers, my screen, my log --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.47,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}都没了\N{\rENG}it's all gone.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我所有的直到652的日志都还在\N{\rENG}But all of my logs up to date 652 still exist.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}备份在主幼儿园的第五切面内\N{\rENG}Backed up in facet 5 of the prime kindergarten.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想让我带你去幼儿园?\N{\rENG}You want me to take you to the kindergarten?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不确定...\N{\rENG}I don't know.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,你不想了解融合簇吗?\N{\rENG}Steven, don't you want to know about the cluster?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯...好吧\N{\rENG}Mm...Okay.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们可以去幼儿园\N{\rENG}We can go to the kindergarten.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,太好了!\N{\rENG}Oh, yes!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但...\N{\rENG}But...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不好,有诈\N{\rENG}No, a catch.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,你的要求是什么?\N{\rENG}Fine. What are your demands?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你得一直抓着我的手\N{\rENG}You're gonna have to hold my hand the whole time.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看,我们到了\N{\rENG}Well, here we are.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,太棒了,我们走\N{\rENG}Okay, great. Let's go.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.11,0:05:56.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里每次来都变得更糟\N{\rENG}This place just gets worse every time I come here.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道,这里的管理太糟糕了\N{\rENG}I know. It's been so poorly managed.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当你第一次孵化出来时\N{\rENG}It must have been in way better shape\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里要好很多吧?\N{\rENG}when you first emerged.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.24,0:06:02.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}孵化?\N{\rENG}Emerged?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错,你算是某种石英,对吧?\N{\rENG}Yeah, you're some kind of Quartz, right?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你一定是在这里制造的\N{\rENG}You must have been made here.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...我是源自我的妈妈和爸爸\N{\rENG}Uh...I came from my mom and dad.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是某种石头吗?或者另一个星球?\N{\rENG}Are those some kind of rocks? Or another planet?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.82,0:06:13.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并不\N{\rENG}Nope.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我爸爸来自地球,而我妈妈是宝石人\N{\rENG}My dad's from earth, but my mom's a gem.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.08,0:06:19.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你算是某种混血?这怎么可能呢?\N{\rENG}You're some sort of hybrid? How is that possible?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}答案在一个故事里,而我将它命名为\N{\rENG}The answer to that is a story I like to call\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"玫瑰和格雷格的罗曼史"\N{\rENG}"the ballad of Rose and Greg."\N
Dialogue: 600,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.11,Hint,,0,0,0,,"the ballad of Rose and Greg"出自披头士的歌名"The Ballad of John and Yoko"
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不在乎\N{\rENG}I don't care.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们赶紧去控制室吧\N{\rENG}Let's just hurry to the control room.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你确定那里安全?\N{\rENG}You sure this is safe?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上次我去那时,\N{\rENG}The last time I was here,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.06,0:06:32.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那里有一堆融合怪物\N{\rENG}there were a bunch of fusion monsters.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错,我之前在检查它们的进展\N{\rENG}Yes, I was checking their progress.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那些是用来干嘛的?\N{\rENG}What's the deal with those things?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.49,0:06:40.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当很明显地球不再是可用的殖民地时,\N{\rENG}When it became clear that the earth was no longer a viable colony,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母世界决定将它用于其它方面-\N{\rENG}homeworld decided to use it for something else --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一系列的实验\N{\rENG}a series of experiments.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个宝石终极武器\N{\rENG}A gem geo-weapon.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,你参与了吗?\N{\rENG}Oh, did you help?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.71,0:06:49.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并没有\N{\rENG}Negative.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没好运生在那个时候\N{\rENG}I wasn't lucky enough to be around for that.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.95,0:06:54.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我浏览了好几百年的报告呢\N{\rENG}But I read over a few hundred years of reports.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要来这里,对吧?\N{\rENG}This is where you need to be, right?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错,我得移开这个面板\N{\rENG}Yes. I'm going to have to remove this panel\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.71,0:07:02.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后做点工作恢复这间屋子的能量供应,\N{\rENG}and do a bit of work to restore power to this room,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.19,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以...我能把手收回来吗?\N{\rENG}so...Can I have my hand back now?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,但呆在我能看见的地方\N{\rENG}Okay, but stay where I can see you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.51,0:07:18.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}完了\N{\rENG}It's over.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没法向你展示任何东西,咱们回吧\N{\rENG}I can't show you anything. Let's go back.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}介意我试试吗?\N{\rENG}Mind if I try?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.77,0:07:23.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上啊\N{\rENG}Go ahead.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}随你便\N{\rENG}Knock yourself out.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.48,0:07:27.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔!\N{\rENG}Whoa!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}走你\N{\rENG}There you go.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.37,0:07:29.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}All right.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.75,0:07:32.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在这里...\N{\rENG}This over here...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}虽然算不上完美,但暂时够用了\N{\rENG}It's not perfect, but it'll do for now.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别呀\N{\rENG}Come on.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么了,小橄?\N{\rENG}What's up, dot?\N
Dialogue: 600,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.93,Hint,,0,0,0,, "What's up, Dot?"出自"What's up, Doc?"，兔八哥的习惯用语
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我够不到-\N{\rENG}I can't quite reach the --.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}寻求帮助没什么不好,你要知道\N{\rENG}It's okay to ask for help, you know.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可以了\N{\rENG}I had it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这些是人工融合的早期尝试\N{\rENG}These are the early attempts at artificial fusion.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.13,0:07:57.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真是好多的宝石碎片啊\N{\rENG}That's a lot of gem shards.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们原来在这里培养它们\N{\rENG}We were growing them here at this very site.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这些只是最终产物的原型而已\N{\rENG}But these were just prototypes for the final product,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.88,0:08:05.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个单独的巨大人工融合体\N{\rENG}a singular giant artificial fusion\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}由几百万的宝石碎片组成\N{\rENG}comprised of millions of gem shards --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.86,0:08:08.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合簇\N{\rENG}the cluster.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.97,0:08:14.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石,你是说现在有个\N{\rENG}Peridot, you're saying there's a giant mutant gem\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}地球那么大的突变宝石人在脚下?\N{\rENG}the size of the earth under us right now?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,不\N{\rENG}Oh, no.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当它最终成型时,比地球可大多了\N{\rENG}When it forms it'll be much, much bigger than the earth.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在它潜伏在地球核心,慢慢孵化\N{\rENG}Right now it lies dormant, incubating in the earth's core.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但当它孵化并产生物质形态时,\N{\rENG}But when it emerges and takes its physical form,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它会摧毁地球\N{\rENG}it will destroy the planet.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}原型已经开始孵化了\N{\rENG}The prototypes are already emerging.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合簇则是下一个\N{\rENG}The cluster is next.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.95,0:08:34.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我们不能离开这个星球,我们就得阻止融合簇\N{\rENG}If we can't get off this planet, we've got to stop the cluster.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我之前觉得这不可行,但我们现在有机会了\N{\rENG}I thought it'd be impossible, but now we have a chance.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是什么?\N{\rENG}What is it?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你呀,史蒂文!\N{\rENG}It's you, Steven!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在你出现了,我们就可以开始工作了\N{\rENG}Now that you're filled in, we can get to work.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...我怎么提供帮助呢?\N{\rENG}Uh...How am I supposed to help?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其实,你已经有了我们所需的所有信息\N{\rENG}Well, you have all the information we need\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有关于地球和它飘忽不定的行为的信息\N{\rENG}about earth and its erratic behavior.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.96,0:08:56.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}将那与我对融合簇丰富的了解相结合,\N{\rENG}Put that together with my expansive knowledge of the cluster,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们也许就能阻止它\N{\rENG}and we just might be able to stop it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,橄榄石,我不认为你想到点子上了\N{\rENG}No, Peridot, I don't think you get it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.51,0:09:03.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只因为我了解云的原理,\N{\rENG}Just because I know how clouds work,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不意味着我知道怎么阻止\N{\rENG}doesn't mean I know how to stop\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个在地球中央的巨大突变体\N{\rENG}a giant mutant in the center of the earth.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.93,0:09:10.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}另外,我知道云和雨的唯一原因\N{\rENG}Besides, the only reason I know anything about clouds and rain\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.06,0:09:11.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是我爸爸告诉我了\N{\rENG}is because my dad told me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你说的是什么?\N{\rENG}What are you talking about?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我原来非常害怕闪电,\N{\rENG}I used to be really scared of thunderstorms,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.71,0:09:16.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}像你一样\N{\rENG}just like you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后我爸爸解释了雨之类的现象是如何发生的,\N{\rENG}Then dad explained how rain and all that stuff works,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后我再也没怕过雨了\N{\rENG}then I wasn't scared of rain anymore.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么,我确定你还有其他的\N{\rENG}Well, I'm sure you have other knowledge\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有关于这个星球如何运作的知识\N{\rENG}about how this planet works.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然,但那些中没有能帮到我们的\N{\rENG}Sure, but none of it's gonna help us.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我们想要阻止融合簇的话,\N{\rENG}If we want to stop this cluster thing,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们就需要水晶战士的帮助\N{\rENG}we'll need help from The Crystal Gems.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我说过我不需要她们!\N{\rENG}I said I don't need them!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们只要传送回我的卫生间就好,\N{\rENG}Let's just warp me back to the bathroom,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者随便你怎么叫的,然后让我们解决这个\N{\rENG}or whatever you call it, and we'll take care of this.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果情况真的变得非常遭,\N{\rENG}If it looks really bad,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么我们只需要向这个爸爸寻求帮助,对不对?\N{\rENG}then we can just ask this dad for help, right?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}咦!那是什么?\N{\rENG}Yipe! What was that?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,不!宝石突变体!\N{\rENG}Oh, no! Gem mutants!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呀!\N{\rENG}Yaah!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}做点什么啊!\N{\rENG}Do something!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在做啊\N{\rENG}I am doing something.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}做点有用的!\N{\rENG}Something useful!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,咱们跑吧\N{\rENG}Uh, let's run.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.80,0:10:01.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来这里\N{\rENG}Over here.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.57,0:10:02.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,那个方向\N{\rENG}No, the other way.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,不是那里\N{\rENG}No, not there.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Aah!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}咱们跑去这个角落吧\N{\rENG}Let's run into this corner.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,不!\N{\rENG}Oh, no!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.28,0:10:09.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们被困在角落里了!\N{\rENG}We're cornered!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.51,0:10:10.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Aah!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!你能摧毁它吗?\N{\rENG}Aah! Can't you destroy it?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,这是我自己能做的全部了\N{\rENG}No, this is all I can do on my own.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呀....\N{\rENG}Yaah...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就这样了,我们完蛋了\N{\rENG}That's it. We are finished.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.02,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&H811CC0&}坚持住,史蒂文\N{\rENG}{\c&H811CC0&}Hang on, Steven.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.15,0:10:28.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}宝石人们!\N{\rENG}It's the gems!\N
