Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石,我们没法\N{\rENG}Peridot, there's no way\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只靠自己阻止这个在地球内的东西\N{\rENG}we can stop this thing in the earth on our own.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们需要水晶战士的帮助\N{\rENG}We need the help of The Crystal Gems.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Steven, are you all right?!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让开,史蒂文\N{\rENG}Move aside, Steven.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.02,0:10:52.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石?\N{\rENG}Peridot?!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们两个在这干嘛?\N{\rENG}What are you two doing here?!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,我记得我告诉你要看住她\N{\rENG}Steven, I thought I told you to keep an eye on her.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.99,0:10:58.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道,但-\N{\rENG}I know, but --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.93,0:11:00.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他只是从犯\N{\rENG}he did what he was told.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.08,0:11:02.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}All right.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着,你们这群草-\N{\rENG}Listen up, you clo--\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}水晶战士\N{\rENG}Crystal gems.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我决定了\N{\rENG}I've made up my mind.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我有些关于融合簇的东西要告诉你们\N{\rENG}I have something to tell you about the cluster.\N
